g.text: Only to be used if the I2C REG is not
populated and the mcu bridge is closed.
If not populated add pulldowns to the 3v3 and 5v EN pins
Pullups can be swapped for lower value if needed
!!!make sure the connected I2C devices don't
have internal pull-ups. Overwise they may cause
high quiecent current and problems with the
connected to the AUX 3v3 and 5v pins!!!
